{"word":"H5288 - נַעַר - naʻar - nah'-ar - Babe","slug":"H5288","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נַעַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>naʻar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>nah'-ar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Babe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05E2;&#x05E8; - na&#x201B;ar</b> - <i>nah'-ar</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5287\">H5287</a>; (concretely) a <i>boy</i> (as active), from the age of infancy to adolescence; by implication a <i>servant</i>; also (by interchange of sex), a <i>girl</i> (of similar latitude in age): - babe, boy, child, damsel [from the margin], lad, servant, young (man)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5271\">H5271</a>, <a href=\"#/H5290\">H5290</a>, <a href=\"#/H5291\">H5291</a>, <a href=\"#/H5292\">H5292</a>, <a href=\"#/H5293\">H5293</a>, <a href=\"#/H5294\">H5294</a>, <a href=\"#/H5295\">H5295</a>, <a href=\"#/H5298\">H5298</a>"}]}